Additionally, it could be categorized as cs.LG (Machine Learning) because it deals with latent variable models. The paper also involves visualization, which could place it in the sub-category of cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper discusses distributed computing, which could place it in the sub-category of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
